org.dcm4cheri.util
Class IntHashtable2

java.lang.Object
  org.dcm4cheri.util.IntHashtable2
public final class IntHashtable2
extends java.lang.Object

Simple internal class for doing hash mapping. Much, much faster than the standard Hashtable for integer to integer mappings, and doesn't require object creation.
If a key is not found, the null is returned. Note: the keys are limited to values above Integer.MIN_VALUE+1.
